thread.title: Melissa Sveticic
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Melissa Sveticic

author: Melissa Sveticic
title: Melissa Sveticic
text:
Bevan helped me very quickly when i booked to collect car at Auckland instead of Wellington. Service was fantastic, car was great, bond returned in less than 24 hours (i had to leave a bond as i only had a debit card, not a credit card)
Staff offered us a lift back to motel on drop off.
Prices were very competitive.
I wouldnt hesitate to recommend this company.
